These are the source files of the Carneades argumentation system.

This software is licensed under the GNU General Public Licence (GLP, v3) and 
the GNU Lesser General Public License (LGPL, v3).  Which license applies 
is specified in the header of each source file.  The licenses are in the 
licenses directory.

The software consists of two main parts: 1) a graphical user interface,
implementated in Java FX; and 2) a collection of R6RS Scheme libraries.  The
source code for these parts are in the gui and engine directories, respectively.

The installation instructions for the Scheme library are in the INSTALL.txt 
file in the engine directory.

For further information see <http://carneades.berlios.de>.

